Preconditions:
- The input array `tasks` must not be null.
- The length of the input array `tasks` must be greater than 0.
- The input integer `sessionTime` must be greater than or equal to the maximum element in the `tasks` array.

Postconditions:
- The output integer must be the minimum number of work sessions needed to finish all the tasks.
- Each task must be completed within a work session.
- A new task can be started immediately after finishing the previous one.
- The tasks can be completed in any order.